          With over 15 years of experience across diverse industries, we've helped hundreds of businesses navigate complex challenges, seize opportunities, and achieve sustainable growth. Our approach combines deep analytical rigor with practical, actionable insights.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400 mb-2">Fortune 500</div>
